{"text_id":153921,"tokens":["How"," to"," Stop"," Being"," Ap","athetic",":"," Break"," the"," Cycle","\n\n","A","pathy"," can"," be"," a"," paraly","zing"," feeling"," that"," makes"," it"," difficult"," to"," find"," motivation"," or"," interest"," in"," anything","."," If"," you","'","re"," struggling"," with"," apathy",","," it","'","s"," time"," to"," break"," the"," cycle"," and"," make"," a"," change","."," Here","'","s"," a"," step","-","by","-","step"," guide"," to"," help"," you"," overcome"," apathy"," and"," start"," living"," the"," life"," you"," want",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","1",":"," Identify"," the"," Root"," Cause"," of"," Your"," A","pathy","**","\n\n","The"," first"," step"," to"," overcoming"," apathy"," is"," to"," identify"," the"," root"," cause"," of"," your"," feelings","."," Is"," it"," due"," to"," depression",","," anxiety",","," or"," boredom","?"," Is"," it"," a"," result"," of"," a"," traumatic"," event"," or"," a"," buildup"," of"," stress","?"," Understanding"," the"," reason"," behind"," your"," apathy"," will"," help"," you"," address"," it"," more"," effectively",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","2",":"," Listen"," to"," Family"," and"," Friends","**","\n\n","Talk"," to"," your"," loved"," ones"," and"," listen"," to"," their"," concerns","."," They"," may"," have"," insights"," into"," your"," behavior"," that"," you","'","re"," not"," aware"," of","."," Be"," open"," to"," their"," feedback"," and"," use"," it"," to"," identify"," patterns"," or"," behaviors"," that"," may"," be"," contributing"," to"," your"," apathy",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","3",":"," Examine"," Your"," Isolation","**","\n\n","Are"," you"," isolating"," yourself"," from"," others","?"," Are"," you"," avoiding"," social"," situations"," or"," spending"," too"," much"," time"," alone","?"," Isolation"," can"," exacerbate"," apathy",","," so"," it","'","s"," essential"," to"," examine"," your"," social"," habits"," and"," make"," changes"," if"," necessary",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","4",":"," Determine"," If"," You","'","re"," Un","fair","ly"," Comparing"," Yourself"," to"," Others","**","\n\n","Comparing"," yourself"," to"," others"," can"," lead"," to"," feelings"," of"," inadequacy"," and"," apathy","."," Stop"," comparing"," yourself"," to"," others"," and"," focus"," on"," your"," strengths"," and"," achievements"," instead",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","5",":"," Examine"," the"," Things"," You"," Used"," to"," Enjoy","**","\n\n","Think"," about"," the"," things"," you"," used"," to"," enjoy"," doing","."," Have"," you"," lost"," interest"," in"," them","?"," Try"," to"," revisit"," those"," activities"," and"," see"," if"," you"," can"," regain"," your"," enthusiasm",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","6",":"," Change"," Your"," Thoughts","**","\n\n","A","pathy"," can"," be"," fueled"," by"," negative"," thoughts"," and"," self","-","talk","."," Change"," your"," thoughts"," by"," focusing"," on"," positive"," affirmations"," and"," self","-","encouragement","."," Replace"," negative"," self","-","talk"," with"," positive"," and"," empowering"," thoughts",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","7",":"," Stop"," Self","-","Lo","athing"," Behaviors"," and"," Thoughts"," of"," I","nade","qu","acy","**","\n\n","Self","-","lo","athing"," and"," thoughts"," of"," inadequacy"," can"," perpetuate"," apathy","."," Stop"," engaging"," in"," behaviors"," that"," make"," you"," feel"," bad"," about"," yourself",","," and"," replace"," them"," with"," positive"," and"," uplifting"," activities",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","8",":"," Be"," the"," First"," Person"," to"," Cong","rat","ulate"," Yourself"," on"," Any"," Job"," Well"," Done","**","\n\n","Celebrate"," your"," achievements",","," no"," matter"," how"," small"," they"," may"," seem","."," Be"," your"," own"," cheerleader"," and"," acknowledge"," your"," progress",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","9",":"," Take"," Action"," by"," Starting"," with"," Small"," Steps","**","\n\n","Break"," down"," your"," goals"," into"," smaller",","," manageable"," steps","."," Taking"," action"," can"," help"," build"," momentum"," and"," motivation",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","1","0",":"," Change"," Your"," Appearance","**","\n\n","Changing"," your"," appearance"," can"," be"," a"," simple"," way"," to"," boost"," your"," mood"," and"," energy","."," Try"," a"," new"," hairstyle",","," get"," a"," haircut",","," or"," update"," your"," wardrobe",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","1","1",":"," Change"," Your"," Bed","time"," and"," Wake","-","Up"," Time","**","\n\n","Establish"," a"," consistent"," sleep"," schedule"," to"," help"," regulate"," your"," mood"," and"," energy"," levels",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","1","2",":"," Exercise"," Your"," Body"," and"," Mind","**","\n\n","Regular"," exercise"," can"," help"," increase"," energy"," and"," motivation","."," Find"," an"," activity"," you"," enjoy",","," whether"," it","'","s"," walking",","," running",","," or"," yoga",","," and"," make"," it"," a"," part"," of"," your"," daily"," routine",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","1","3",":"," Monitor"," Your"," Diet","**","\n\n","Eat"," a"," balanced"," diet"," that"," includes"," plenty"," of"," fruits",","," vegetables",","," whole"," grains",","," and"," lean"," protein","."," A"," healthy"," diet"," can"," help"," improve"," your"," mood"," and"," energy"," levels",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","1","4",":"," Make"," Bigger"," Shifts"," in"," Thinking"," and"," Actions","**","\n\n","Once"," you","'","ve"," made"," small"," changes",","," it","'","s"," time"," to"," think"," bigger","."," Consider"," making"," significant"," changes"," to"," your"," life",","," such"," as"," switching"," jobs",","," relocating",","," or"," ending"," toxic"," relationships",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","1","5",":"," Stay"," Busy","**","\n\n","Keep"," yourself"," occupied"," with"," activities"," you"," enjoy","."," Staying"," busy"," can"," help"," distract"," you"," from"," feelings"," of"," apathy"," and"," boredom",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","1","6",":"," Design"," a"," Routine"," That"," Works"," for"," You","**","\n\n","Create"," a"," daily"," routine"," that"," includes"," time"," for"," work",","," rest",","," and"," play","."," A"," consistent"," routine"," can"," help"," provide"," structure"," and"," motivation",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","1","7",":"," Commit"," to"," Changing"," Your"," Outlook"," and"," Behaviors","**","\n\n","Make"," a"," commitment"," to"," yourself"," to"," change"," your"," outlook"," and"," behaviors","."," Write"," it"," down"," and"," post"," it"," somewhere"," visible"," to"," remind"," yourself"," of"," your"," goals",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","1","8",":"," Execute"," Your"," Plan","**","\n\n","Put"," your"," plan"," into"," action"," and"," start"," making"," changes","."," Break"," it"," down"," into"," smaller"," steps"," and"," focus"," on"," one"," step"," at"," a"," time",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","1","9",":"," Identify"," Your"," First"," Positive"," Activity","**","\n\n","Identify"," one"," activity"," that"," brings"," you"," joy"," and"," makes"," you"," feel"," good","."," Make"," time"," for"," it"," in"," your"," daily"," routine"," and"," use"," it"," as"," a"," motiv","ator",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","2","0",":"," Adjust"," for"," Imper","f","ections","**","\n\n","Remember"," that"," you","'","re"," not"," perfect",","," and"," it","'","s"," okay"," to"," make"," mistakes","."," Adjust"," your"," plan"," as"," needed"," and"," don","'","t"," be"," too"," hard"," on"," yourself"," when"," you"," encounter"," setbacks",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","2","1",":"," Acknowledge"," Your"," Progress","**","\n\n","Celebrate"," your"," progress",","," no"," matter"," how"," small","."," Acknowledge"," the"," changes"," you","'","ve"," made"," and"," the"],"sub_source":"wikihow","model":"llama3-70b","label":1}